nodes.text: Rogan B.B. Cham was a male HoloNet News reporter and secret Rebel spy during the Galactic Civil War. Cham was instrumental in aiding his contacts in the Rebel Alliance in their successful attempt to kill Grand Moff Torith and steal a D-Wing Space Superiority Fighter from the Cynestra Space Craft Show above the planet Cynestra during the Galactic Civil War.
